| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Projection: vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer).id, vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer).answer, trunc(vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer)._score,Int64(3))                                                             |
|               |   Sort: vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer)._score DESC NULLS FIRST, vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer).id ASC NULLS LAST, fetch=4                                                                                               |
