|               |       TableScan: vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer) projection=[_score, answer, id]                                                                                                                                                         |
| physical_plan | ProjectionExec: expr=[id@0 as id, answer@1 as answer, trunc(vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer)._score,Int64(3))@2 as trunc(vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer)._score,Int64(3))]                                                 |
