|               |     SortExec: TopK(fetch=4), expr=[_score@3 DESC, id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |       ProjectionExec: expr=[id@2 as id, answer@1 as answer, trunc(_score@0, 3) as trunc(vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer)._score,Int64(3)), _score@0 as _score]                                                                            |
|               |         RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |           ProjectionExec: expr=[_score@1 as _score, answer@2 as answer, id@0 as id]                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |             HashJoinExec: mode=CollectLeft, join_type=Left, accumulator=MinMaxLeftAccumulator, on=[(id@0, id@1)], projection=[id@0, _score@1, answer@2]                                                                                                 |
